#. module: cyllo_subscription
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:cyllo_subscription.field_sale_order_template__invoice_creation
msgid ""
"Choose a invoice creation method, (Manually:- Invoices must be manually "
"created if the manual invoice creation option is selected.; Draft:- A draft "
"invoice is created if the draft option for invoice creation is selected; "
"Confirmed:- If the Confirmed invoice generating mode is selected, a draft "
"invoice is generated and automatically changes to the confirmed state when a"
" daily scheduled action is executed. Sent:- If Sent is selected, at the time"
" of order confirmation, a mail is sent to the consumer)"
msgstr ""
"Elija un método de creación de facturas (Manual: Las facturas deben crearse "
"manualmente si se selecciona la opción de creación manual; Borrador: Se "
"crea una factura en borrador si se selecciona la opción de borrador; "
"Confirmada: Si se selecciona el modo de generación de factura confirmada, se "
"genera una factura en borrador que cambia automáticamente al estado confirmado "
"cuando se ejecuta la acción programada diaria; Enviada: Si se selecciona Enviada, "
"al confirmar el pedido se envía un correo al cliente)."

